<p>15 May 1915<br/>Saturday</p>
<p>All parties doing well. the A L H lose a lot of men, in their eagerness to outdo the infantry they put their heads above the parapet   &amp;  get  <u>hit</u><br/>This is a place where you learn most by the mistakes of others, because the one who makes the mistake does not learn any more, he gets planted.</p>
<p>1915 May 16<br/>Sunday<br/>Sunday After Ascension</p>
<p>Get a new visitation in the shape of a few 8 &frac12; inch high power shells which burst w/- a tremendous explosion but do comparatively no damage except break down a few barricades   &amp;  kill one or two men</p>
